    "[`<details>`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details) 允许折叠内容，[`<summary>`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary) 为内容指定可见标题。\n\n这对于 FAQ、可折叠章节或任何可切换的内容都很有用。"
